365
00:25:17,671 --> 00:25:19,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

366
00:25:20,775 --> 00:25:22,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membantu sebisaku.</font>

367
00:25:24,678 --> 00:25:26,247
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti capek. Istirahatlah.</font>

368
00:25:27,648 --> 00:25:29,984
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak secapek itu, kok.</font>

369
00:25:31,051 --> 00:25:33,254
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tidak lapar?
Mau makan sesuatu?</font>

370
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:37,124
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat dirimu. Kita baru saja
selesai makan ayam.</font>

371
00:25:38,225 --> 00:25:42,396
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, iya ya. Aku pasti sudah lupa.
Cuacanya panas sekali.</font>

372
00:25:43,297 --> 00:25:44,465
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu karena kau lelah.</font>

373
00:25:44,665 --> 00:25:46,634
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuklah. Aku juga permisi.</font>

374
00:25:46,967 --> 00:25:47,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

375
00:25:54,074 --> 00:25:55,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuklah sekarang.</font>

376
00:25:58,879 --> 00:26:02,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kira aku mengatakan itu karena
aku lapar?</font>

377
00:26:14,395 --> 00:26:15,996
<font color=#FFFF00>Suara apa sih sepagi ini?</font>

378
00:26:18,666 --> 00:26:19,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada yang pindah ke rumah sebelah?</font>

379
00:26:27,074 --> 00:26:28,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Lampu gantung?</font>

380
00:26:28,976 --> 00:26:30,077
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa pengantin baru?</font>

381
00:26:38,118 --> 00:26:40,754
<font color=#FFFF00>Ho Bang. Kenapa kau keluar dari sana?</font>

382
00:26:40,754 --> 00:26:42,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu? Aku baru pindah ke sini.</font>

383
00:26:42,923 --> 00:26:44,592
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Pindah ke sini?</font>

384
00:26:45,326 --> 00:26:46,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Ke sebelah rumahku?</font>

385
00:26:47,361 --> 00:26:49,563
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga tidak tinggal di sini sendirian.</font>

386
00:26:49,897 --> 00:26:51,866
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku punya teman serumah sekarang.</font>

387
00:26:51,866 --> 00:26:53,434
<font color=#FFFF00>Benarkah? Siapa?</font>

388
00:26:54,401 --> 00:26:55,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuletakkan di mana, ya ini?</font>

389
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:00,341
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Sung!</font>

390
00:27:02,476 --> 00:27:03,544
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo, Jung Won.</font>

391
00:27:03,577 --> 00:27:04,812
<font color=#FFFF00>"Halo, Jung Won"?</font>

392
00:27:04,845 --> 00:27:06,947
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei. Apa kalian serius?</font>

393
00:27:07,348 --> 00:27:09,984
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kalian pindah ke sebelah
tanpa memberitahuku?</font>

394
00:27:10,117 --> 00:27:12,686
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah kubilang 'kan Jung Won akan
tetap menyambut kita..</font>

395
00:27:12,686 --> 00:27:14,855
<font color=#FFFF00>walaupun kita tidak bilang akan pindah
ke sebelah rumahnya?</font>

396
00:27:14,955 --> 00:27:17,124
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Benar. Kau baik sekali, Jung Won.</font>

397
00:27:17,124 --> 00:27:20,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, kalian ini benar-benar tidak masuk akal.</font>

398
00:27:21,328 --> 00:27:23,264
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa semuanya sudah masuk?</font>

399
00:27:24,231 --> 00:27:26,133
<font color=#FFFF00>Ho Bang, ini kutaruh di mana, ya?</font>

400
00:27:28,135 --> 00:27:29,637
<font color=#FFFF00>Pokoknya, selamat datang.</font>

401
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:35,442
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kalian bawa barang banyak sekali?</font>

402
00:27:35,976 --> 00:27:37,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Biaya sewa di Seoul benar-benar mahal.</font>

403
00:27:37,945 --> 00:27:41,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Waktu aku tinggal di Chungho, aku
bisa memasukkan semua barangku ke dalam rumah.</font>

404
00:27:42,917 --> 00:27:46,186
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Rococo, baroque, vintage,</i></font>

405
00:27:46,620 --> 00:27:47,721
<font color=#FFFF00>dan Noryangjin?</font>

406
00:27:49,456 --> 00:27:50,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini dari zaman Joseon?</font>

407
00:27:51,425 --> 00:27:53,193
<font color=#FFFF00>Kacau sekali.</font>

408
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:57,197
<font color=#FFFF00>Jung Won, tidak gampang mengumpulkan
semua ini.</font>

409
00:27:57,364 --> 00:27:58,766
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong hargai seleraku.</font>

410
00:27:59,833 --> 00:28:02,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, mau kau letakkan di mana ini?</font>

411
00:28:02,670 --> 00:28:05,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Itu jam dinding.</font>

412
00:28:05,606 --> 00:28:08,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku butuh dinding untuk
meletakkannya.</font>

413
00:28:09,410 --> 00:28:10,811
<font color=#FFFF00>Jung Won, apa kau tidak butuh jam?</font>

414
00:28:11,578 --> 00:28:13,414
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ini 'kan kecil.
- Apa?</font>

415
00:28:13,847 --> 00:28:16,650
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jamnya 'kan kecil.
- Sudah tidak muat di rumahku.</font>

416
00:28:16,650 --> 00:28:17,651
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kalian bicarakan?</font>

417
00:28:18,052 --> 00:28:20,454
<font color=#FFFF00>Buang saja. Apaan sih ini? Yang benar saja.</font>

418
00:28:20,454 --> 00:28:21,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini jam alarm loh.</font>

419
00:28:22,022 --> 00:28:23,357
<font color=#FFFF00>- Benarkah?
- Ya.</font>

420
00:28:23,590 --> 00:28:24,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pamit.</font>

421
00:28:25,159 --> 00:28:26,860
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sampai jumpa.
- Sampai jumpa.</font>

422
00:28:26,860 --> 00:28:29,163
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dah.
- Sampai jumpa.</font>

423
00:28:30,464 --> 00:28:31,832
<font color=#FFFF00>Tambahkan bawang putih di sini.</font>

424
00:28:32,166 --> 00:28:34,168
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bawang putih?
- Ya. Bawang merah juga.</font>

425
00:28:48,649 --> 00:28:51,151
<font color=#FFFF00>Kak, coba cicipi ini.</font>

426
00:28:55,222 --> 00:28:56,357
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebih enak dari yang pertama.</font>

427
00:28:56,490 --> 00:28:58,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sama dengan yang tadi.</font>

428
00:28:58,859 --> 00:29:01,261
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang sebelumnya enak.
Yang ini juga enak.</font>

429
00:29:02,863 --> 00:29:04,064
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf, Ji Soo.</font>

430
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:07,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pergi dulu.</font>

431
00:29:07,935 --> 00:29:08,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat malam.</font>

432
00:29:12,573 --> 00:29:14,641
<font color=#FFFF00>- Terima kasih.
- Nikmati makananmu.</font>

433
00:29:23,951 --> 00:29:27,488
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sujebi</i> di sini simpel
tapi..</font>

434
00:29:27,554 --> 00:29:28,689
<font color=#FFFF00>tetap enak.</font>

435
00:29:29,590 --> 00:29:31,392
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuahnya dibuat dari teri.</font>

436
00:29:31,992 --> 00:29:35,195
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa merasakan terinya,
