438
00:29:44,038 --> 00:29:45,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa merasakan semuanya?</font>

439
00:29:46,507 --> 00:29:48,942
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutku kuahnya enak,</font>

440
00:29:49,610 --> 00:29:52,079
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi adonan <i>sujebi</i>-nya adalah kunci terpenting.</font>

441
00:29:53,580 --> 00:29:54,615
<font color=#FFFF00>Memangnya apa?</font>

442
00:29:54,915 --> 00:29:55,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Tepung kacang.</font>

443
00:29:56,383 --> 00:29:57,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Tepung kacang?</font>

444
00:29:57,751 --> 00:30:01,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, tepung kacang, adonanya kaya rasa..</font>

445
00:30:01,388 --> 00:30:03,157
<font color=#FFFF00>dan jadi lebih kenyal.</font>

446
00:30:04,124 --> 00:30:05,125
<font color=#FFFF00>Benarkah?</font>

447
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:09,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi ada pasta yang rasanya mirip
